text: Lieutenant-Colonel Lewis Phillips Winby (1874-1956) was Conservative MP for Harborough from 1924 to 1929. ==Sources== *Leigh Rayment's Historical List of MPs *Whitaker's Almanack, 1925 to 1929 editions *Craig, F.W.S.
